From 58e467bed7ffeecb41769b6e6ddc4ebd0795574a Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Alok Singh <aloksing@qti.qualcomm.com>
Date: Fri, 18 Jul 2025 17:36:53 +0530
Subject: [PATCH 3/3] UPSTREAM: DP: wifi: ath12k: Enable non compaction on qcn
 platform

Currently qcn platform handles only compact tlv structure for below tlvs.
1. MPDU START
2. MSDU END
3. PPDU END USER STATS

When packet log is enabled, compaction for above TLVs will get disabled
Hence enabling non-compact tlv handling on qcn platform.

Initializing hal_mon_ops for MPDU_START, MSDU_END, PPDU_END_USER_STATS
with wrapper functions to handle compact and non-compact tlvs both,
Compare received tlv len and sizeof non compact tlv structure to call
function to handle compact/non-compact TLV parsing.

Patch-dependency:
	0446-0002-UPSTREAM-DP-wifi-ath12k-Add-compact-ppdu-end-user-st.patch

Signed-off-by: Alok Singh <aloksing@qti.qualcomm.com>
